caption:
Fresh off a stellar NCAA season, @sharp__jackson joined HOKA @naz_elite, adding major depth to our professional team’s track roster. Join us in welcoming Jackson to HOKA! 

With a fantastic collegiate career behind him, Jackson is now looking to level up on the world stage. In between training sessions in Flagstaff, Jackson shared why he’s excited to join the team, what he learned this season, and his goals as a professional runner. Check out the blog through the link in our profile. 

Photos: @clippedinmedia
